===Noun===
# (''proper noun'') Traditional British [[ice cream]]. An [[ice-cream cornet]] with a [[Cadbury's]] [[Flake]] [[chocolate]] bar inserted, typically at a 60-degree angle. Usually made with soft, rather than scooped, ice cream. Also known as a [[99 Flake]].
# A wafer cone designed for ice cream manufactured by Askey’s.

